data.description: This great home ticks all the boxes for excellent livability, with several high-value upgrades to improve quality of life, such as hard-wearing laminate flooring, top-quality appliances, built-in shelving, water filter and softener to protect plumbing, and tankless gas water heater for those endless showers. The large family room allows for plenty of layout and entertaining options. Tucked into the desirable, well kept Sequoia Grove neighborhood, the home is situated on an ample lot, with a large back yard full of potential, and backing to open church grounds behind. This home will fulfill your Idaho Dreams!
